name: Rachael Eubanks

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: Celebrating Money in Her Pocket week and #WomensHistoryMonth with a visit to @OldTownGrace, a woman-owned small business specializing in unique jewelry, clothing and formal dresses. I am always asked where I bought this necklace and now have one for a gift. #MoneyinMIPocket  https://t.co/eyvvG3L04Y

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: Tripling the Earned Income Tax Credit will pull 22,000 Michiganders out of working poverty and deliver 730,000 households an average combined tax refund of $3,000. We’re with @GovWhitmer. Let’s get this done. #MIBudget

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: We agree, @GovWhitmer: retirees deserve to keep their hard-earned money. Let’s repeal the retirement tax and save half a million households $1,000 a year. #MISOTS22

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: Repealing the retirement tax can save half a million households an average of $1,000 per year. I’m ready to work with @GovWhitmer to get this done. #MISOTS22

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: I went online to #ShopLocal today! #DYK: for every dollar spent at a #MISmallBusiness, 67¢ stay in the local community? Places such as ⁦@PlaymakersFit⁩ are pillars in EL/Okemos. I’m proud to stand with ⁦@GovWhitmer⁩ to support #SmallBusinessSaturday.  https://t.co/2eyeASqRe1

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: It’s a great day to patronize a veteran-owned business like the Okemos and East Lansing @BaskinRobbins locations! The EL store even has a drive thru. I highly recommend the pistachio or butter pecan. #VeteransDay  https://t.co/2VCSITc3AP

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: Did you know that military members, veterans and their spouses and kids are eligible to receive financial benefits like income and property tax relief and tuition assistance? It’s a few of the ways Michigan honors the service of military families. Thank you Veterans! #VeteransDay

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: It’s primary day, Michigan! If you didn’t vote absentee like I did, polls are open today from 7am to 8pm. If you’re not registered yet, it’s not too late! You can find out how and your polling location here:  https://t.co/lMk4Xuy02T #MichiganPrimary #Vote #MIGov  https://t.co/bhG5gYf2ll

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: In the words of @LtGovGilchrist, the most rewarding part of my multi-disciplinary career has been for more people to see themselves in leadership positions in their neighborhoods, cities, and state. I’m eternally grateful to @GovWhitmer and @onetoughnerd for that chance. #MIGov

name: Rachael Eubanks

As a bonus, I got to see @MI_DTMB testify at the Committee on Homeland Security & Govt Affairs. #NASTDC #MIGov  https://t.co/0j6hC5ETFa

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: Calling all Spartans! A great opportunity to put your financial talents to work at @MiTreasury to help build a better Michigan. #GoGreen #MIGov

name: Rachael Eubanks
tweet: I spent an incredible #MLKDay2020 volunteering at @HavenHouseEL with @GovWhitmer and family, @laradirector and daughter and @HeidiWashington. I’m grateful we have a safe place in the Lansing/EL community where families can go for help and stay together during times of transition.
